title: Kasman Piano Duo to Premiere in Performing Arts Series (Lee University)
text: ( Source : Lee University ) The Lee University School of Music Performing Arts Series will welcome the Kasman piano duo, comprising Yakov Kasman and his daughter Aleksandra “ Sasha ” Kasman, on Friday, Oct. 30 at 7:30 p.m. in Squires Recital
